### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = {{auth_login.response.body.accessToken}}

### Create Income Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Freelance Web Design",
  "description": "Income from freelance web design projects",
  "color": "#4CAF50",
  "icon": "computer",
  "type": "INCOME"
}

### Create Expense Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Supermercado",
  "description": "Compras no supermercado",
  "color": "#F44336",
  "icon": "shopping-cart",
  "type": "EXPENSE"
}

### Get All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Categories by Type (Income)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?type=INCOME
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Categories by Type (Expense)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?type=EXPENSE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Specific Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{category_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Category
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{category_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Freelance Updated",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "color": "#2196F3"
}

### Setup Default Categories
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories/setup-defaults
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete Category
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{category_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

